{"tid":974403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"排名最易上床日本女大生　　正妹發起連署逼周刊道歉","createTime":"2019-01-09T00:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T07:43:30.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db4bfe10944e13b0e347ad2b836826ceb92b6d92","tid":974403,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:04:51.000Z","msg":"日本八卦雜誌《週刊SPA!》在去年12月25日出刊的刊物中，其中一篇內容主打「最易上床女大生排名」，此文一出立刻引發爭議，更有女大生發起連署抵制周刊，獲得廣大迴響。而《週刊SPA!》也在昨日出面道歉，但沒有表態會不會下架回收該期刊物。<br />\n<br />\n《週刊SPA!》在內容中指出，現在日本大學流行男女生一起開飲酒趴，或者男生出錢邀女生來狂歡，酒後一定會出現「約砲」或「撿屍」等狀況，而周刊內容就主打「最容易跟男生上床的女大生排名」。內容指出，第1名最好「征服」的女大生學校，是實踐女子大學，其次為大妻女子大學、菲利斯女學院大學、法政大學和中央大學。內容更表示，最容易被上的女生的外型，其共通點包括喜歡留中長黑髮、淡妝、提著中型包包，以及穿著素雅、微露香肩的造型。<br />\n但此報導一出，立刻引發爭議，有不少日本鄉民批評這是在物化女性，就讀國際基督教大學的女大生山本一奈(音譯)，<a href=\"http://更是在Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8Change.org&d=Q7xW9EaYSPylzTvpwZPTJTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=23502607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更是在Change.org</a>網站發起連署活動，要求雜誌道歉及停售該期周刊。截至目前為止，已有超過3.4萬人支持山本的連署活動，《週刊SPA!》也在昨日被逼得出面道歉，承認文章內容冒犯觀眾，有嘩眾取寵的問題，但至於會不會下架該期周刊，《週刊SPA!》未給出明確答案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190109/1497330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190109%2F1497330&d=Q7xW9EaYSPylzTvpwZPTJTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0032da37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190109%2F1497330&h=8d697f19\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190109/1497330</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190109/640_e206bcc5301c24c06987de17a879d18e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190109%2F640_e206bcc5301c24c06987de17a879d18e.jpg&h=dbcdb9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190109/640_2d1315914779f0fb76212e3b5766852a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190109%2F640_2d1315914779f0fb76212e3b5766852a.jpg&h=b17e512a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一飲酒就預扑野，幾happy"},{"pid":"74b564c5597af8aaf2a1d4ddb8dce67b7f11bdcb","tid":974403,"uid":53254,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:07:20.000Z","msg":"講中咗先咁大反應"},{"pid":"d536d257a9ede8118478c60e2933d43b44f5dbe8","tid":974403,"uid":123264,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:08:20.000Z","msg":"死臭雞 敢做唔敢認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4967fc553a2bff3a6b85e178ce593e78762521a","tid":974403,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:09:03.000Z","msg":"唔怪得有時d華人女學生去到日本會被人殺害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe13a5cfefaa813aabab6bc92526ea2895c3835","tid":974403,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:09:42.000Z","msg":"日本旅遊指南？<br />\n要去齊頭三位嘅大學"},{"pid":"4212e19e22db251620200308ed8656e49b01b9c4","tid":974403,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:11:23.000Z","msg":"黑白鬼去依3間大學附近Ｄ吧揾食，一定屌到怕"},{"pid":"fda44c6a70164c0dd32e3a68e4811d96e9f0b40a","tid":974403,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74b564c5597af8aaf2a1d4ddb8dce67b7f11bdcb","tid":974403,"uid":53254,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:07:20.000Z","msg":"講中咗先咁大反應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7ba83b8ff65f1e69d6b5e46fde3794a05b9f32","tid":974403,"uid":178072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"女權自助餐<br />\n<br />\n<b